#Shuttering routes to shutter and unshutter a microservice

PATCH       /service-shuttering/true            com.cjwwdev.shuttering.controllers.ShutteringController.shutter()
PATCH       /service-shuttering/false           com.cjwwdev.shuttering.controllers.ShutteringController.unshutter()
GET         /service-shuttering/state           com.cjwwdev.shuttering.controllers.ShutteringController.getShutterState()